From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Buildroot <buildroot@buildroot.org>
Date: Wed, 1 Jul 2026 02:06:00 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] arm: dts: build elpass U-Boot device tree

Buildroot copies board/rhodesisland/elpass/dts/elpass-uboot.dts into
arch/arm/dts through BR2_TARGET_UBOOT_CUSTOM_DTS_PATH and builds U-Boot
with DEVICE_TREE=elpass-uboot.

Register the resulting dtb in the Zynq dtb list so U-Boot's dts build can
produce arch/arm/dts/elpass-uboot.dtb.

Signed-off-by: Buildroot <buildroot@buildroot.org>
---
 arch/arm/dts/Makefile | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/arch/arm/dts/Makefile b/arch/arm/dts/Makefile
--- a/arch/arm/dts/Makefile
+++ b/arch/arm/dts/Makefile
@@ -221,6 +221,7 @@ dtb-$(CONFIG_ARCH_UNIPHIER_SLD8) += \
 	uniphier-sld8-ref.dtb
 
 dtb-$(CONFIG_ARCH_ZYNQ) += \
+	elpass-uboot.dtb \
 	bitmain-antminer-s9.dtb \
 	zynq-cc108.dtb \
 	zynq-cse-nand.dtb \
-- 
2.50.0
